title: God Given Desires | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: God Given Desires | Joel Osteen
description:
When you keep God first place, He will place dreams inside you that lead you to your destiny. You can trust Him to guide you to the best plan for your life. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
